    "text": "Claude code channels lets you proxy Claude Code into an app! Its fricken awesome. With Lopecode you can have a local file it can use its native tools with, but then I also let it attach watch variables to the notebook so it can make modification in-app and see the live results. Its phenomenal. Claude has an escape hatch to native web, Lopecode is a sandboxed safehouse for code. Claude can push to git, its works way better than I expected. Claude can refresh the page when it makes big changes.",
